Author: ageofdadz
Text: I get that, and I hate looking at old pictures of me at my LW too. I try to remember that’s not my peak body!! That body wasn’t healthy and couldn’t carry me safely through daily tasks. It caused me a lot of pain and embarrassment with symptoms.

Author: throwaway199502
Text: Always me. I’m ALWAYS looking at my old pictures and it’s truly the top trigger. Like u can look at thin celebs for days but the moment you see you .. like that... that’s what does it for me
